# Copy this file to brand_local.tf to document your branding customizations.
#
# The main brand resource is in brand.tf. To customize branding:
#
# Option 1: Upload custom assets
#   Upload your logo, favicon, and background to Authentik with filenames:
#   - logo.png (or your preferred name)
#   - favicon.png
#   - background.jpg
#   Then update brand.tf with your filenames.
#
# Option 2: Use Authentik web UI
#   Go to System > Brands and customize branding there.
#   Note: Terraform may overwrite web UI changes on next apply.
#
# Option 3: Modify brand.tf directly
#   Change the branding_* attributes in brand.tf to your values.
# =============================================================================

